# get the particles in a loop, are these in the same organization as write file? Compare with that script

nexpt = "NATL"
npath = '/glade/p/work/chsharri/Cms-master/expt/' + nexpt + '/expt_' + nexpt + '/output/'

# need to make a loop here
nfiles = 5

nfile = 'traj_file_1.nc'
cmsdata = nc.Dataset(npath+nfile,'r')
plon = cmsdata.variables['lon'][:]
plat = cmsdata.variables['lat'][:]

for ifile in range(2,nfiles+1):
    nfile = 'traj_file_'+str(ifile)+ '.nc'
    cmsdata = nc.Dataset(npath+nfile,'r')
    plon = np.concatenate((plon,cmsdata.variables['lon'][:]), axis = 0)
    plat = np.concatenate((plat,cmsdata.variables['lat'][:]), axis = 0)

plat.shape
Out[7]:
(33824, 61)
